rComments: After class with Sandy, your life will never be the same.  She is the SWEETEST and nicest lady, and she built our class into a community and family.  She is truly the most positive aspect of my career in the College of Education.  She completely prepared me for success in student teaching and the professional world.  SANDY ROCKS!

Her CI classes are super easy- as long as you come to class you'll get at least a B. Few exams, and she tells you the answers ahead of time. Super awesome though b/c she's so nice and would never say a bad thing about anybody. ever.
Wonderful, wonderful professor!! Such a sweet lady :)
